2026-04-20T17:35:53.399Z JOY-00FC-1D comment.added "Plan: Extend 'joy project member add' to: (1) require --passphrase of the acting manage member, (2) generate a random OTP, store Argon2id hash in otp_hash, print the OTP to stdout for out-of-band delivery, (3) sign attestation over email + capabilities + otp_hash using the acting member's identity key, (4) write attestation to the new member's entry. Tightly coupled with JOY-0072 (OTP redemption flow)." [ai:claude@joy delegated-by:horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
2026-04-20T17:35:53.408Z JOY-0072 comment.added "Plan: Extend joy auth with --otp flag. 'joy auth --otp CODE --passphrase NEW' verifies OTP against otp_hash, derives Argon2id key from new passphrase, sets the member's public_key and salt, clears otp_hash, establishes a session. Implementation shares core with joy auth init but entry gate is OTP rather than 'this is my first time'. Tightly coupled with JOY-00FC-1D (OTP generation side)." [ai:claude@joy delegated-by:horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
